{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_31","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"for f in src/design_patterns/symbiont_mediated_perturbation_of_host_process src/design_patterns/symbiont_mediated_activation_of_host_process src/design_patterns/symbiont_mediated_suppression_of_host_process; do printf '%s\\\\n' \\\"\"'$f\"; sed -n '\"'1,220p' \\\"\"'$f\"; done'","aggregated_output":"src/design_patterns/symbiont_mediated_perturbation_of_host_process\npattern_name: symbiont-mediated perturbation of host process\n\npattern_iri: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/go/patterns/symbiont_mediated_perturbation_of_host_process.yaml\n\ndescription: >-\n   This pattern is for classes representing perturbation by symbiont of a host process differentiated by the process impacted. \n\nclasses:\n  biological process: \"GO:0008150\"\n  biological regulation: \"GO:0065007\"\n\nrelations: \n  regulates in another organism: \"RO:0012010\"\n\nvars:\n  entity: \"'biological process'\"\n\nname:\n     text: \"symbiont-mediated perturbation of %s\"\n     vars:\n       - entity\n\ndef:\n  text: \"A process in which a symbiont alters or subverts the normal execution of a host %s.\"\n  vars:\n     - entity\n\nequivalentTo:\n  text: \"'symbiont-mediated perturbation of host process' and 'regulates in another organism' some %s\"\n  vars:\n    - entity\nsrc/design_patterns/symbiont_mediated_activation_of_host_process\npattern_name: symbiont-mediated activation of host process\n\npattern_iri: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/go/patterns/symbiont_mediated_activation_of_host_process.yaml\n\ndescription: >-\n   This pattern is for classes representing activation by symbiont of a host process differentiated by the process impacted. \n\nclasses:\n  biological process: \"GO:0008150\"\n  biological regulation: \"GO:0065007\"\n\nrelations: \n  positively regulates in another organism: \"RO:0012013\"\n\nvars:\n  entity: \"'biological process'\"\n\nname:\n     text: \"symbiont-mediated activation